    difficulty: 'easy',
    timeTargetSeconds: 60,
    mistakeType: 'concept error',
    questionType: 'multiple_choice',
    stimulus: 'The boreal forest, also called the taiga, stretches across northern Canada, Russia, and Scandinavia _______ it is the largest terrestrial biome on Earth, covering approximately 17 million square kilometers.',
    question: 'Which choice completes the text so that it conforms to the conventions of Standard English?',
